{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 2021, "height": 2813, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "text", "block_content": "花园头文杰小黑成留根留小留丰收大民小民丰贵南坻坞小军上西村杜锦杜坑正军兴智云伟云峰治国忠智焕军明坤虎留振涛振信虎林虎民建民杜窑政哲\n", "block_bbox": [160, 501, 1671, 714], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "各一百元", "block_bbox": [163, 716, 345, 777], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "东张村保现七十元", "block_bbox": [163, 848, 561, 918], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "杜窑建华振华留军留成松民伟民忠民安民成强东明东起东升东强东晓发民宏民成民治安保安治军学军全军红涛青玉成玉怀玉富玉宝生宝民宝勤宝群新民永民杜华治民来福留福群福玉强永强晨阳晨亮润民\n", "block_bbox": [162, 986, 1674, 1250], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "东张村平现西现令均改伟明学明均红伟宗贤建伟宗诗各四十元\n", "block_bbox": [160, 1459, 1530, 1593], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "东张村军伟延伟二均松伟栓劳宗奎各三十元\n东张村天明丽红各二十元\n\n窑湾兰英十元\n\n", "block_bbox": [163, 1667, 1247, 1872], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "友人捐助：\n仁村乡杨鸿杰黄世民火洼侯景朝各二百元\n仁村乡郑雪朝一百元\n\n", "block_bbox": [160, 1952, 1070, 2150], "block_id": 6, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [1776, 733, 1858, 1444], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "六", "block_bbox": [1792, 2130, 1846, 2206], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 9}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.5887212753295898, "coordinate": [160.451904296875, 1952.1956787109375, 1070.9223